net.visualcoding.ts3serverquery.event

Class TS3MessageEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.visualcoding.ts3serverquery.event.TS3Event
      • net.visualcoding.ts3serverquery.event.TS3MessageEvent

  • public class TS3MessageEvent
extends TS3Event
    This class represents a message sent to the server query client from the Teamspeak 3 server. This message may be one of three modes: private, server, or channel. Modes are representing using the TS3MessageEvent#Mode enum.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Aldehir Rojas
